## Auto-mode permission boundaries — graduated trust by action class
direction: down

intro: {
  shape: text
  label: "Not all agent actions are equally risky.\nClassify actions, then auto-allow safe ones,\ngate medium-risk, REQUIRE approval for dangerous."
  style.italic: true
  style.font-color: "#7c3aed"
}

tiers: {
  direction: right

  auto: {
    label: "AUTO-ALLOW\n(no prompt)"
    shape: rectangle
    style.fill: "#bbf7d0"
    style.stroke: "#16a34a"
    body: {label: "Examples:\n• Read files in workspace\n• Search the web\n• Run linter / formatter\n• Open IDE panels\n• Query allowlisted APIs\n\nProperty: REVERSIBLE,\nlow-impact, no data leak"; shape: text}
  }

  notify: {
    label: "NOTIFY + AUTO\n(toast / log, agent proceeds)"
    shape: rectangle
    style.fill: "#fef3c7"
    style.stroke: "#d97706"
    body: {label: "Examples:\n• Write/edit files in workspace\n• Install dev dependencies\n• Run tests\n• Local-only side effects\n\nProperty: REVERSIBLE in seconds,\nlimited to workspace"; shape: text}
  }

  gate: {
    label: "GATE\n(prompt before action)"
    shape: rectangle
    style.fill: "#fed7aa"
    style.stroke: "#ea580c"
    body: {label: "Examples:\n• git commit / push\n• Shell commands with elevated perms\n• Modify config / env\n• Cross-system writes\n\nProperty: hard to reverse\nor visible to other parties"; shape: text}
  }

  approve: {
    label: "REQUIRE APPROVAL\n(blocking; explicit OK)"
    shape: rectangle
    style.fill: "#fecaca"
    style.stroke: "#dc2626"
    body: {label: "Examples:\n• Deploy to prod\n• Money-moving / payment\n• Send external email\n• Delete data / drop tables\n• Change permissions / IAM\n• Force-push, rewrite history\n\nProperty: IRREVERSIBLE\nor high externalities"; shape: text}
  }
}

defaults: {
  label: "Recommended defaults"
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#dbeafe"
  style.stroke: "#2563eb"
  body: {label: "• Configure once, persist in repo / project config\n• Per-user overrides\n• Clear list of which actions are which tier\n• Log everything (even auto-allowed)\n• Easy 'always approve' / 'always deny' learning\n• Allow 'temporary YOLO mode' for trusted contexts"; shape: text}
}

intro -> tiers
tiers -> defaults
